N.P. 
<bibRefCitation id="1422BDF95953FFF3FBCF8D9DFB5E19EB" author="Taylor, N. P. &amp; Zappi, D. C." box="[1069,1261,1189,1211]" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" pagination="256 - 258" refId="ref1800" refString="Taylor, N. P. &amp; Zappi, D. C. (2020) Nomenclatural adjustments in Brazilian Cereeae (Cactaceae). Phytotaxa 470 (3): 256 - 258. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 470.3.6" type="journal article" year="2020">Taylor (2020: 256)</bibRefCitation>
