<taxonomicName id="B7B3BB8B5953FFF3FE1A8F33FC921B73" authorityName="Guiggi" authorityYear="2020" box="[504,801,1547,1571]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Cactaceae" genus="Melocactus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="neoviridescens">
<emphasis id="42C71C1A5953FFF3FE1A8F33FC921B73" bold="true" box="[504,801,1547,1571]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="97">Melocactus neoviridescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
:―This taxon was elevated at specific rank based on both morphological characters, and its ecology and chorology which well allow to distinguish it from 
<taxonomicName id="B7B3BB8B5953FFF3FB688F17FA181B17" box="[1162,1451,1583,1607]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Cactaceae" genus="Melocactus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="97" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pachyacanthus">
